    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J519">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>'Twas warm --  at first -- like Us --</l>
                    <l>Until there crept upon</l>
                    <l>A Chill -- like frost upon a Glass --</l>
                    <l>Till all the scene -- be gone.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Forehead copied Stone --</l>
                    <l>The Fingers grew too cold</l>
                    <l>To ache -- and like a Skater's Brook --</l>
                    <l>The busy eyes -- congealed --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>It straightened -- that was all --</l>
                    <l>It crowded Cold to Cold --</l>
                    <l>It multiplied indifference --</l>
                    <l>As Pride were all it could --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And even when with Cords --</l>
                    <l>'Twas lowered, like a <app type="revision"><lem>Freight</lem><rdg>Freight</rdg></app>
Weight --</l>
                    <l>It made no Signal, nor demurred,</l>
                    <l>But dropped like Adamant.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                </lg>

            </div>     
